Feed Your Wild Side

Good Source of Protein

Protein is an essential part of your diet and Jack Link’s Beef Jerky is a delicious way to get more every day. With 11g of protein and only 80 calories per serving, it’s a must-have snack to help keep you satisfied and energized all day.

Perfect Portable Snacks

How did ancient civilizations fuel themselves to build pyramids or win sword battles? Meat. If it worked for them, Jack Link’s beef jerky can definitely help you power through a late day at work, tackle your honey-do list or fuel a workout.

Made with 100% Premium Beef*

Jack Link’s Beef Jerky is made from lean cuts of 100% premium beef*, then seasoned with simple ingredients like water and salt. Our delicious beef jerky is 96% fat free with no added MSG**

Product Description

Think way back. Like even before that. Ancient civilizations fueled themselves with meat. If it worked for them, it can definitely help you power thru. You may not be crossing treacherous seas, but endless to-dos, kid activities and trying to squeeze in a workout can feel just like it. Jack Link's Teriyaki Beef Jerky is a delicious combination of East meets West delicious. Each strip is made with 100% premium beef that is marinated with our special blend of soy, garlic, ginger and brown sugar. Then, it's slow cooked over hardwood smoke for the perfect smoky flavor. Packed with 10g of protein per serving, it's 96% fat free and has no added MSG**, nitrates or nitrites. The result? A taste kids of all ages enjoy.It's enough to satisfy the entire family! Share a bag on family movie night, bring it to the soccer game for a snack or toss a bag in the car for when the whole gang is hungry. When we open a bag it hardly lasts three minutes, but once open, be sure to refrigerate or eat your beef jerky within three days.. **Except for that naturally occurring in soy sauce

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
